===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Iris (Masters)}}
Iris, as the [[Unova]] {{pkmn|Champion}}, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Iris|Haxorus}}, {{p|Hydreigon}}, {{p|Naganadel}}, {{p|Druddigon}}, and {{p|Lapras}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Iris became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with her joining the {{player}} after completing the ninth chapter of the [[PML arc]].

Iris has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the PML arc.

